                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.9327/11–2047: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-12-02T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 2, 1947—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1454. Dept will comment at length points Urtel 2261, Nov 20 in few days. Desire
                    confirmation last date consultation may begin under terms Art 11, and comments
                    re advisability holding consultation Nanking with Jarvis assisting Emb.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lovett</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
